e some of the most successful pirates/buccaneers of all time, hated and feared by the Spanish."}, "latest_revision": 12, "revision": 12, "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2008-09-15T16:41:21.453722"}, "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2025-10-21T16:47:02.229159"}}, {"publishers": ["McBooks Press", "Distributed by Login Trade"], "number_of_pages": 286, "isbn_10": ["0935526455"], "subject_place": ["Caribbean Area"], "pagination": "286 p. ;", "covers": [714034], "lc_classifications": ["PR6037.A2 C35 1998b", "PR6037.A2C35 1998b"], "key": "/books/OL353173M", "authors": [{"key": "/authors/OL2687190A"}], "publish_places": ["Ithaca, N.Y", "Chicago"], "genres": ["Fiction."], "source_records": ["marc:marc_records_scriblio_net/part27.dat:66067753:871", "marc:marc_loc_updates/v35.i15.records.utf8:3248656:972", "marc:marc_loc_2016/BooksAll.2016.part27.utf8:8825139:972", "bwb:9780935526455"], "title": "Captain Blood", "dewey_decimal_class": ["823/.912"], "identifiers": {"goodreads": ["1083383"], "librarything": ["45462"]}, "languages": [{"key": "/languages/eng"}], "lccn": ["98012825"], "subjects": ["Pirates -- Fiction", "Physicians -- Fiction", "British -- Caribbean Area -- Fiction", "Caribbean Area -- Fiction"], "publish_date": "1998", "publish_country": "nyu", "series": ["Classics of nautical fiction series"], "by_statement": "by Rafael Sabatini.", "works": [{"key": "/works/OL8070950W"}], "type": {"key": "/type/edition"}, "latest_revision": 14, "revision": 14, "created": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2008-04-01T03:28:50.625462"}, "last_modified": {"type": "/type/datetime", "value": "2025-03-28T15:31:17.153075"}}, {"title": "Captain Blood", "subtitle": "his Odyssey", "authors": [{"key": "/authors/OL2687190A"}], "publish_date": "1922", "publishers": ["Houghton Mifflin company"], "pagination": "437 p. :", "by_statement": "by Rafael Sabatini; with frontspiece by N.C. Wyeth.", "publish_places": ["Boston ; New York"], "type": {"key": "/type/ed